```plantuml
@startuml becloudway_serverless-data-pipeline

actor User
participant "Public API" as API
participant "RetrieveXMLTrafficData" as XMLRetriever
participant "S3 (Raw XML)" as S3XML
participant "TransformTrafficDataToJson" as XML2JSON
participant "S3 (JSON)" as S3JSON
participant "PublishTrafficData" as Publisher
participant "Kinesis Stream" as Kinesis
participant "StreamProcessor" as Processor
participant "Kinesis Analytics" as Analytics
participant "Kinesis Firehose" as Firehose
participant "S3 (Processed)" as S3Processed
participant "DynamoDB (Analytics)" as DDB1
participant "DynamoDB (Alerts)" as DDB2
participant "AlertSaver" as AlertSave
participant "AlertSender" as AlertSend
participant "Slack" as Slack
participant "Flask API" as Flask
participant "PowerBI" as PowerBI

User -> API: Request traffic data
API -> XMLRetriever: XML response
XMLRetriever -> S3XML: Store raw XML
S3XML -> XML2JSON: Trigger on new object
XML2JSON -> S3JSON: Store converted JSON
S3JSON -> Publisher: Trigger on new object
Publisher -> Kinesis: Publish traffic events
Kinesis -> Processor: Stream data
Processor -> Kinesis: Filtered data
Kinesis -> Analytics: Process in real-time
Analytics -> Firehose: Send analytics results
Firehose -> S3Processed: Store processed data
Analytics -> DDB1: Store real-time analytics
DDB1 -> AlertSave: Trigger on stream
AlertSave -> DDB2: Store alerts
DDB2 -> AlertSend: Trigger on stream
AlertSend -> Slack: Send alert
AlertSend -> Flask: Send alert
Publisher -> PowerBI: Forward data

@enduml
```